HEADWORD: calming
<hw>calming</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>tending to soothe or
calm or tranquilize.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ataractic, ataraxic, sedative, soothing,
tranquilizing.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>freeing from fear and anxiety.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> assuasive, pacifying, soothing.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Calmly</ent>⟦br⟧
